Major Cross Streets are Valencia Road and Kolb RoadBedrooms: 3Bathrooms: 2Sq. Footage: 1,467Pet & Smoking Policy: Pets considered on a case-by-case basis, No Smoking
 No Application Fees! Newer 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single level Tucson home located in La Estancia De Tucson. This open floor plan home features tile flooring and all high traffic areas, neutral paint throughout and upgraded window blinds. Upgraded kitchen featuring granite countertops and backsplash, separate pantry, gas range, stove top microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator. This is a split-level floor plan with a primary suite a larger primary suite with walk in closet, double sink vanity and dual shower and step in shower. Washing machine and dryer is included and easy to maintain desert landscaping.No Application Fees! 12 Month Minimum Lease. Security Deposit is equal to one month's rent. See our criteria to rent for qualifications.All fully completed applications with all required information are reviewed and processed in the order that they are received. Processing time is typically 1-2 business days provided applicants submit all required items. Incomplete applications and any missing documents are considered incomplete and are set aside until completed. $300 refundable cleaning deposit applies. Refundable pet deposit would apply for approved pets. Pet deposits are typically a minimum of $300 per pet and will vary based on type, size, breed, age and other relevant items. We do not charge up front application fees; however, tenants to pay $40 per applicant to run background screening as we near the end of the screening process. Tenants to pay 2.9% monthly administrative fee in addition to monthly City Transaction Privilege Tax (Sales Tax). Contact us for more details.Available to show by appointment.Denali Real Estate, LLCSCAM ALERTDenali Real Estate is the only authorized Agent to list this home for rent. If you find this website listed on any website by someone other than Denali Real Estate, it is likely a scam. Please report this directly to us.

Smoking allowed:No
